```py
class Queue: 
def __init__(self): 
        self.head = None 
        self.tail = None 
        self.count = 0 
```

```py
    def enqueue(self, data): 
        new_node = Node(data, None, None) 
        if self.head is None: 
            self.head = new_node 
            self.tail = self.head 
        else: 
            new_node.prev = self.tail 
            self.tail.next = new_node 
            self.tail = new_node 

        self.count += 1 
```

```py
def dequeue(self): 
current = self.head 
        if self.count == 1: 
            self.count -= 1 
            self.head = None 
            self.tail = None 
        elif self.count > 1: 
            self.head = self.head.next 
            self.head.prev = None 
            self.count -= 1 
```

        while self.count > 0: 
            current_track_node = self.dequeue() 
            print("Now playing {}".format(current_track_node.data.title))
